arStrings.szText: Using an {c_important}Agility{/c} Skill reduces the Cooldown of your next {c_important}Subterfuge{/c} Skill by {c_number}[Affix_Value_1|%|]{/c}. Using a {c_important}Subterfuge{/c} Skill increases the damage of your next {c_important}Agility{/c} Skill by {c_random}[Affix_Value_2|%x|]{/c}.

{c_important}Agility{/c} Skills reduce the Cooldown of {c_important}Subterfuge{/c} Skills by {c_number}[Affix_Value_1|%|]{/c}. {c_important}Subterfuge{/c} Skills increase the damage of {c_important}Agility{/c} Skilsl by {c_random}[Affix_Value_2|%x|]{/c}.
